{"tid":2244294,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麻辣鮑魚雞煲","createTime":"2020-10-15T11:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T15:57:59.000Z","uid":239860,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"245a06f8fd579d9c25d67f49ee9d031f450ead10","tid":2244294,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"呢排好忙，冇咩時間出片，今日終於整完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次煮左麻辣鮑魚雞煲，有一年雞煲好流行，於是就出去食，食完之後就返屋企自己整，我覺得幾好味，同出面差不多，但可能同出面既做法唔同，畢竟係我自己食完再調味。有興趣可以睇下條片，鍾意既可以訂閱埋我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xUk-qakRqOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxUk-qakRqOg&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugziZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=2dfeb32d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xUk-qakRqOg</a><br />\n製成品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NP2xiU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNP2xiU3.jpg&h=749045e8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nD雞要煎下去先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cLbzts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cLbzts.jpg&h=621aa754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教埋個醬汁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ea0yNOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fea0yNOy.jpg&h=2da47d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後炒埋一齊<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00x5DVf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00x5DVf.jpg&h=02f73b0d&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n煮完就可以好似平時出面食咁煲下煲下<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪好簡單呢<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以訂閱埋我FACEBOOK 同IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/captopuskitchen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcaptopuskitchen&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugziZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=698bad09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/captopuskitchen</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/catopuskitchen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcatopuskitchen%2F&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugziZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=7136aa9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/catopuskitchen/</a><br />\n多謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285f4cceb400a655bbe651e33070f684883ebcce","tid":2244294,"uid":49577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3396ffc1fa6756ac9b76e8d3198fbd8183fda2af","tid":2244294,"uid":272819,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"鮑魚放落雞煲會不會好曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c65b967ac7ce85b04ad630e698f934e26f61fc","tid":2244294,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"有無得加水打邊爐"},{"pid":"c905d1cd9c8b5e7f7e3c203c0de5a38ac1bcee75","tid":2244294,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d907651a1c2bbb871d189572d1830e9fa242bb26","tid":2244294,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"285f4cceb400a655bbe651e33070f684883ebcce","tid":2244294,"uid":49577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:23:55.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />估唔到咁耐冇出都有1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012868af56d2484920832262324489fda2689d4c","tid":2244294,"uid":239860,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3396ffc1fa6756ac9b76e8d3198fbd8183fda2af","tid":2244294,"uid":272819,"like":8,"dislike":